graph TD
    subgraph DevMachine[" "]
        CLI["Command Line Interface (cicd)<br/>Entry point for commands"]
        Git["Git Repository<br/>(.pipelines/*.yaml)"]
        
        subgraph Controller["Controller Service"]
            Validator["Validation Engine"]
            Orchestrator["Pipeline Orchestrator"]
            Reporter["Report Generator"]
        end
        subgraph JobQueue["Job Queue"]
            MQ["Job Queue"]
        end
        subgraph ExecutorPool["Job Executors Pool"]
            Exec1["Job Executor 1<br/>(Thread/Process)"]
            Exec2["Job Executor 2<br/>(Thread/Process)"]
            ExecN["Job Executor N<br/>(Thread/Process)"]
        end
        
        Docker["Docker Engine"]
        
        subgraph DockerContainers["Docker Containers"]
            Cont1["Container 1<br/>(Job Image)"]
            Cont2["Container 2<br/>(Job Image)"]
            ContN["Container N<br/>(Job Image)"]
        end
        
        DB["PostgreSQL Database<br/>- pipeline_runs<br/>- stages<br/>- jobs<br/>- execution_logs"]
    end
    
    CLI <-->|Read YAML| Git
    CLI -->|Commands| Controller
    
    Controller -->|Validate| Validator
    Controller -->|Orchestrate| Orchestrator
    Controller -->|Schedule| Scheduler
    Controller -->|Generate Reports| Reporter
    
    Scheduler -->|Dispatch Jobs| ExecutorPool
    ExecutorPool -->|Job Status| Scheduler
    
    Exec1 & Exec2 & ExecN -->|Docker API| Docker
    
    Docker -->|Manage| DockerContainers
    
    Controller <-->|Store/Query| DB
    ExecutorPool -->|Log Results| DB
    
    style CLI fill:#e1f5ff
    style Controller fill:#fff4e1
    style ExecutorPool fill:#e8f5e9
    style Docker fill:#f3e5f5
    style DB fill:#ffe0e0